headline: AI helps Canadian entrepreneurs compete with big business finds GoDaddy
summary: New research reveals that Canadian microbusiness owners are embracing Generative (Gen) AI tools to help run their businesses, with two thirds (61%) of entrepreneurs using the technology in the past few months alone.
